snippet.title: acoustic car session: “how did you find me” (original)
snippet.description:
Here is another original song, “how did you find me?” written about 3 years ago. Hope you enjoy, sending all the love❤️

Lyrics:

How did you find me?
It’s like it was a dream
I know it sounds cheesy
But I think it was destiny 
And I’m going to be blunt 
Cause I want you and me

Cause no one loves me like you love me
And no one’s treated me like you do
And no one stays, they all go away
Cause no one stays but you 

And how did you find me?
In this 21st century
You make it so easy 
I’m high off you, you’re my ecstasy 
And I’m going to be blunt 
Cause I want you and me

Cause no one loves me like you love me
And no one’s treated me like you do 
And no one stays, they all go away
Cause no one stays but you 

No one stays but you 
No one stays but you.
